#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.precision_recall_fscore_support.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.precision\\_recall\\_fscore\\_support"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:1 of
msgid "Compute precision, recall, F-measure and support for each class"
msgstr "计算每个类的精度、召回率、F值和支持度"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:3 of
msgid ""
"The precision is the ratio ``tp / (tp + fp)`` where ``tp`` is the number "
"of true positives and ``fp`` the number of false positives. The precision"
" is intuitively the ability of the classifier not to label as positive a "
"sample that is negative."
msgstr ""
"精度是比率 ``tp / (tp + fp)``，其中 ``tp`` 是真正例的数量，``fp`` 是假"
"正例的数量。直观上，精度是分类器不将负样本标记为正的能力。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:8 of
msgid ""
"The recall is the ratio ``tp / (tp + fn)`` where ``tp`` is the number of "
"true positives and ``fn`` the number of false negatives. The recall is "
"intuitively the ability of the classifier to find all the positive "
"samples."
msgstr ""
"召回率是比率 ``tp / (tp + fn)``，其中 ``tp`` 是真正例的数量，``fn`` 是假"
"负例的数量。直观上，召回率是分类器找出所有正样本的能力。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:12 of
msgid ""
"The F-beta score can be interpreted as a weighted harmonic mean of the "
"precision and recall, where an F-beta score reaches its best value at 1 "
"and worst score at 0."
msgstr ""
"F-beta 分数可以被解释为精度和召回率的加权调和平均数，其中 F-beta 分数在 1"
" 时达到最佳值，在 0 时最差。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:16 of
msgid ""
"The F-beta score weights recall more than precision by a factor of "
"``beta``. ``beta == 1.0`` means recall and precision are equally "
"important."
msgstr ""
"F-beta 分数通过因子 ``beta`` 给予召回率比精度更高的权重。``beta == 1.0`` "
"表示召回率和精度同样重要。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:19 of
msgid "The support is the number of occurrences of each class in ``y_true``."
msgstr "支持度是 ``y_true`` 中每个类出现的次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:21 of
msgid ""
"If ``pos_label is None`` and in binary classification, this function "
"returns the average precision, recall and F-measure if ``average`` is one"
" of ``'micro'``, ``'macro'``, ``'weighted'`` or ``'samples'``."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``pos_label is None`` 且是二分类任务，当 ``average`` 是 ``'micro'``"
"、``'macro'``、``'weighted'`` 或 ``'samples'`` 之一时，此函数返回平均精度"
"、召回率和 F 值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:25 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:27 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:29 of
msgid "Estimated targets as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "分类器返回的估计目标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:31 of
msgid "The strength of recall versus precision in the F-score."
msgstr "F 分数中召回率与精度的权重比。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:33 of
msgid ""
"The set of labels to include when ``average != 'binary'``, and their "
"order if ``average is None``. Labels present in the data can be excluded,"
" for example to calculate a multiclass average ignoring a majority "
"negative class, while labels not present in the data will result in 0 "
"components in a macro average. For multilabel targets, labels are column "
"indices. By default, all labels in ``y_true`` and ``y_pred`` are used in "
"sorted order."
msgstr ""
"当 ``average != 'binary'`` 时要包括的标签集，以及当 ``average is None`` "
"时的顺序。数据中存在的标签可以被排除，例如在计算多类平均值时忽略多数负类"
"；而在数据中不存在的标签在宏平均时将导致 0 成分。对于多标签目标，标签是列"
"索引。默认情况下，``y_true`` 和 ``y_pred`` 中的所有标签都按排序后的顺序"
"使用。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:41 of
msgid ""
"The class to report if ``average='binary'`` and the data is binary. If "
"the data are multiclass or multilabel, this will be ignored; setting "
"``labels=[pos_label]`` and ``average != 'binary'`` will report scores for"
" that label only."
msgstr ""
"当 ``average='binary'`` 且数据为二分类时要报告的类别。如果数据是多类或多"
"标签，此设置将被忽略；若设置 ``labels=[pos_label]`` 并且 ``average != '"
"binary'``，则仅报告该标签的得分。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:46 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If ``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:  ``'binary'``:"
"     Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``.     "
"This is applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary. "
"``'micro'``:     Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true "
"positives,     false negatives and false positives. ``'macro'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted     mean.  "
"This does not take label imbalance into account. ``'weighted'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted     by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This     alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an     F-score "
"that is not between precision and recall. ``'samples'``:     Calculate "
"metrics for each instance, and find their average (only     meaningful "
"for multilabel classification where this differs from     "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类的得分。否则，此参数确定在数据上执行的平均"
"类型：``'binary'``：仅报告 ``pos_label`` 指定的类的结果。仅适用于目标（``"
"y_{true,pred}``）为二元的情况。``'micro'``：通过计算总的真正例、假负例和"
"假正例来全局计算指标。``'macro'``：为每个标签计算指标，并求其未加权的"
"平均值。不考虑类别不平衡。``'weighted'``：为每个标签计算指标，并根据支持"
"度（每个标签的真实实例数）进行加权平均。这会调整“macro”以考虑类别不平衡"
"；它可能导致 F 分数不在精度和召回率之间。``'samples'``：为每个样本计算"
"指标，并求其平均值（仅对多标签分类有意义，此时不同于 :func:`accuracy_"
"score`）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:46 of
msgid ""
"If ``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:"
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类别的分数。否则，这将确定对数据执行的平均类型"
"："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:49 of
msgid "``'binary'``:"
msgstr "``'binary'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:50 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``. This is "
"applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary."
msgstr ""
"仅报告由 ``pos_label`` 指定的类别的结果。这仅在目标 (``y_{true,pred}``) "
"为二分类时适用。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:52 of
msgid "``'micro'``:"
msgstr "``'micro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:53 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true positives, false "
"negatives and false positives."
msgstr "通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例来全局计算指标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:55 of
msgid "``'macro'``:"
msgstr "``'macro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:56 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted mean.  This "
"does not take label imbalance into account."
msgstr "计算每个标签的指标，并找到它们的未加权平均值。这不考虑标签不平衡问题。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:58 of
msgid "``'weighted'``:"
msgstr "``'weighted'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:59 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an F-score that "
"is not between precision and recall."
msgstr ""
"计算每个标签的指标，并根据支持度（每个标签的真实实例数）计算它们的加权"
"平均值。这会修改 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；结果可能得到不在精确率和召回率"
"之间的 F 分数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:63 of
msgid "``'samples'``:"
msgstr "``'samples'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:64 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each instance, and find their average (only "
"meaningful for multilabel classification where this differs from "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:68 of
msgid ""
"This determines which warnings will be made in the case that this "
"function is being used to return only one of its metrics."
msgstr "这确定在使用此函数仅返回其中一个指标时将发出哪些警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:71 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:73 of
msgid ""
"Sets the value to return when there is a zero division:    - recall: when"
" there are no positive labels    - precision: when there are no positive "
"predictions    - f-score: both  If set to \"warn\", this acts as 0, but "
"warnings are also raised."
msgstr ""
"设置在零除时返回的值：    - recall：当没有正标签时    - precision：当没有"
"正预测时    - f-score：两者皆是  如果设置为 \"warn\"，则行为与 0 相同，但"
"也会引发警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:74 of
msgid "Sets the value to return when there is a zero division:"
msgstr "设置发生零除时要返回的值："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:75 of
msgid "recall: when there are no positive labels"
msgstr "召回率：当没有正标签时"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:76 of
msgid "precision: when there are no positive predictions"
msgstr "精确率：当没有正预测时"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:77 of
msgid "f-score: both"
msgstr "f分数：两者都是"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:79 of
msgid "If set to \"warn\", this acts as 0, but warnings are also raised."
msgstr "如果设置为 \"warn\"，这将作为 0 处理，但也会发出警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:82 of
msgid ""
"* **precision** (*float (if average is not None) or array of float, shape"
" =        [n_unique_labels]*) * **recall** (*float (if average is not "
"None) or array of float, , shape =        [n_unique_labels]*) * "
"**fbeta_score** (*float (if average is not None) or array of float, shape"
" =        [n_unique_labels]*) * **support** (*None (if average is not "
"None) or array of int, shape =        [n_unique_labels]*) -- The number "
"of occurrences of each label in ``y_true``."
msgstr ""
"* **precision** (*float (如果 average 不为 None) 或浮点数组，形状 =      "
"  [n_unique_labels]*) * **recall** (*float (如果 average 不为 None) 或"
"浮点数组，形状 =        [n_unique_labels]*) * **fbeta_score** (*float ("
"如果 average 不为 None) 或浮点数组，形状 =        [n_unique_labels]*) * *"
"*support** (*None (如果 average 不为 None) 或整数数组，形状 =        [n_"
"unique_labels]*) -- ``y_true`` 中每个标签的出现次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:82 of
msgid ""
"**precision** (*float (if average is not None) or array of float, shape ="
"        [n_unique_labels]*)"
msgstr ""
"**precision** (*float (如果 average 不为 None) 或浮点数组，形状 =        "
"[n_unique_labels]*)"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:83 of
msgid ""
"**recall** (*float (if average is not None) or array of float, , shape ="
