#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_recall_fscore_support:124
#: of
msgid ""
"When ``true positive + false positive == 0``, precision is undefined; "
"When ``true positive + false negative == 0``, recall is undefined. In "
"such cases, by default the metric will be set to 0, as will f-score, and "
"``UndefinedMetricWarning`` will be raised. This behavior can be modified "
"with ``zero_division``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``true positive + false positive == 0`` 时，精确率未定义；当 ``true "
"positive + false negative == 0`` 时，召回率未定义。在这些情况下，默认度量"
"将设为 0，F 分数也是如此，并会引发 ``UndefinedMetricWarning``。此行为可以"
"通过 ``zero_division`` 修改。"

